dc_description_s: These polygon and point data layers represent parks for Green County, Wisconsin in 2017. They are feature classes within the geodatabase, Green_Parks_2017.gdb. The features included in the geodatabase are 'GREEN_PARKS_UNK_PNT' and 'GREEN_PARKS_UNK_POLY'.
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements. For complete metadata documentation please visit http://www.co.green.wi.gov/localgov_departments_details.asp?deptid=115&locid=148 .This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.[SUPPLIED DATA AS POLYGONS AND POINTS, WHICH ARE NOT DERIVATIVES OF EACH OTHER, BUT FROM SEPARATE SOURCES.THIS DATASET HAS NOT BEEN MAINTAINED AND SOURCES ARE GENERALLY UNKNOWN.]
